Compilation flags:
========================================
Enable : HYDRO
Disable: PARTICLE, GRAVITY


Default setup:
========================================
1. BOX_SIZE = 1kpc
2. simulation time = 100 Myr
3. Units: in cgs
4. Enable SRC_EXACTCOOLING


Note:
========================================
1. This test problem is for testing the exact cooling scheme (reference: Farber et al. 2018)
2. Modify the source term ExactCooling to have only one branch of the cooling function
3. The analytical solution and simulation error will be recorded in Output__Error file when OPT__OUTPUT_USER is enabled.
4. plot_ExactCooling.py is for plotting the evolution of temperature.

